scenes.description: Amelia chats with the audience about her trip to Japan, including stories about moss, shopping, and going to an arcade with Kiara and Mumei.
A 'waiting...' screen featuring a claw machine animation and BGM, with brief interjections from Amelia as she sets up the fan book.
Amelia returns to chat, thanking the audience and preparing to look at the fan-made birthday book.
